05:34.287 --> 05:35.619
Oh, your breath smells like Pop Tarts.

05:35.655 --> 05:38.822
- What's for breakfast? I'm starving.
- Coffee smells great.

05:38.858 --> 05:41.258
If you are going to be
staying here temporarily,

05:41.294 --> 05:42.660
