but you are stupid manager.

13:15.850 --> 13:17.316
I save us.

13:17.352 --> 13:18.784
Now weave money for our family.

13:18.820 --> 13:21.187
Well, we want it back.
And I'm not stupid.

13:21.222 --> 13:22.621
You didn't know the difference between

13:22.657 --> 13:24.590
adoption papers and sales documents.

13:24.625 --> 13:26.826
Wordy stuff confuses me,
and it's not the same.

13:26.861 --> 13:28.861
And taking our bar is way
worse than being stupid.

13:28.896 --> 13:31.130
It's cunty.

13:31.165 --> 13:33.432
Overdraft charges on many checks,

13:33.468 --> 13:36.035
penalties for late taxes, no insurance,

13:36.070 --> 13:38.838
