18:50.661 --> 18:52.761
[sniffs twice] Ah!

18:55.099 --> 18:56.932
Ready, Clyde?

18:56.967 --> 18:58.333
Let's roll, Bonnie.

18:59.856 --> 19:02.370
Am I happy to see you today, Gallagher.

19:02.406 --> 19:04.072
