19:04.108 --> 19:07.356
Been a long night of training
a bunch of uninspired dipshits.

19:10.581 --> 19:12.314
You good?

19:12.349 --> 19:14.282
Yeah. Yeah.

19:14.318 --> 19:15.951
Crazy morning.

19:18.522 --> 19:19.788
