19:21.992 --> 19:23.325
Fuck prom.

19:23.360 --> 19:25.327
I'm recommending you to train next time.

19:25.362 --> 19:26.928
You could do these in your
sleep, plus, it'll look

19:26.964 --> 19:28.930
