if you ever want to advance.

19:28.966 --> 19:30.398
- [alarm chimes]
- Cool, thanks.

19:30.434 --> 19:32.100
- Oh, okay.
- [indistinct PA announcement]

19:32.136 --> 19:33.702
Let's ride.

19:47.217 --> 19:49.684
I'm not feeling good.

19:49.720 --> 19:51.186
Are you fucking shitting me?

19:51.221 --> 19:52.187
You're sick?

19:52.222 --> 19:53.688
[retches]

19:53.724 --> 19:55.257
- Think I'm gonna puke.
- Just go.

19:55.292 --> 19:56.825
