20:15.345 --> 20:17.646
- Son of a...
- [laughs]

20:17.681 --> 20:19.814
- I...
- Okay, listen.

20:19.850 --> 20:21.516
So when you light the fire,

20:21.518 --> 20:23.318
I'm gonna Taser the guard,

20:23.353 --> 20:25.620
