20:34.865 --> 20:37.532
[sniffs] Ah.

20:37.568 --> 20:39.401
All right.

20:39.436 --> 20:41.203
[breathes deeply]

20:41.238 --> 20:43.171
[exhales]

20:43.207 --> 20:44.573
Yes.

20:44.608 --> 20:49.578
