20:49.613 --> 20:51.012
Move those feet, bitch!

20:51.048 --> 20:52.914
- Now, walk!
- Shit. No-no-no-no.

20:52.950 --> 20:54.749
- Those guys look agitated.
- Yeah.

20:54.785 --> 20:56.751
Eric didn't say anything
about a SWAT team.

20:56.787 --> 20:58.086
- Did Eric use his own product?
- Yeah.

20:58.121 --> 20:59.793
- Hey!
- Yes, sir?

20:59.818 --> 21:01.590
Where the fuck are your clothes?

21:01.625 --> 21:04.092
I... um... I was robbed, sir.

21:04.127 --> 21:05.660
- You were robbed?
- They forced me to strip.

21:05.696 --> 21:07.495
- Yeah.
- Wh-where might I report that?

21:07.531 --> 21:08.744
Level one.

21:08.769 --> 21:11.166
- Level one!
- Level one, thank you, sir!

21:11.201 --> 21:14.202
<i>♪ rock music ♪</i>

21:14.238 --> 21:19.207
