21:56.113 --> 21:58.046
Well, we could just pack her
stuff up and take it to her.

21:58.081 --> 22:00.315
Or throw it out the
window. That's cool too.

22:00.350 --> 22:02.050
How'd it go at the bar?

22:02.085 --> 22:03.385
- Is she dead yet?
- [sighs]

22:03.420 --> 22:05.287
Svetlana wants us to
keep being a thrupple

22:05.322 --> 22:06.621
and work for her at The Alibi.

22:06.657 --> 22:08.390
[scoffs]

22:08.425 --> 22:10.325
