22:24.975 --> 22:26.741
Hey, that looks like my T-shirt.

22:26.777 --> 22:28.610
And-and-and that's my elephant!

22:28.645 --> 22:31.156
V, are you even pulling
from the right drawer?

22:31.181 --> 22:32.211
Where the matches?

22:32.236 --> 22:33.682
On the table right there.

22:33.717 --> 22:35.016
Wait, why?

22:35.052 --> 22:37.747
Lighter fluid? Downstairs.

22:42.059 --> 22:43.792
Hey. Where is he?

22:43.827 --> 22:46.728
[scoffs] Barely functioning.

22:52.069 --> 22:53.201
Hey.

22:53.236 --> 22:54.803
What's going on?

22:54.838 --> 22:57.339
Nothing. What's with you?

22:57.374 --> 22:59.741
[dishes clatter]

23:02.245 --> 23:05.447
