23:18.895 --> 23:20.962
[sarcastic chuckle]

23:20.997 --> 23:23.398
Oh, yeah? Fire me for what, huh?

23:23.433 --> 23:26.067
For not wiping the bread crumbs
out of the booths well enough

23:26.103 --> 23:28.536
or for not cleaning the
bacon grease off the grill

23:28.572 --> 23:30.004
with expert fucking detail?

23:30.040 --> 23:31.806
