pay or you can fire me.

23:44.921 --> 23:47.455
Huh? You're the boss, big sis.

23:52.729 --> 23:55.063
Yes! Check cashing hole

23:55.098 --> 23:57.031
ought to be good for some cash.

23:57.067 --> 23:58.833
Couple of security cameras.

23:58.869 --> 24:00.769
It's perfect!

24:02.703 --> 24:05.203
We gotta wait until the place clears.

24:07.611 --> 24:09.444
You sure these aren't loaded?

24:09.479 --> 24:12.781
Yeah, I filled 'em with rock salt.

24:12.816 --> 24:15.884
Rock salt? [sniffs]

24:15.919 --> 24:18.686
[both groan]

24:18.722 --> 24:20.889
[groaning] Oh, God! Yeah!

24:20.924 --> 24:21.923
[grunts]

24:21.958 --> 24:25.727
[both groaning and grunting]

24:25.762 --> 24:28.129
[energetic grunting]

24:28.165 --> 24:29.831
[sighs]

24:32.769 --> 24:35.603
Frankie, it's like old times.

24:35.639 --> 24:37.806
[chuckles]

24:44.948 --> 24:48.057
- [van door slides open]
- Motherfucker!

24:48.082 --> 24:49.425
[van door slides shut]

24:49.450 --> 24:50.849
[grunts]

24:53.490 --> 24:55.757
Fuck you!

24:55.792 --> 24:58.460
I'll fucking... fucking kill you.

24:58.495 --> 24:59.706
[panting]

25:19.216 --> 25:21.149
The fuck is with the blindfold?

25:21.184 --> 25:23.651
The fuck's with you being late, bitch?

25:28.825 --> 25:30.658
[chuckles]

25:32.896 --> 25:35.663
You like the high school bleachers?

25:35.699 --> 25:37.732
Our spot, man.

25:42.906 --> 25:46.508
Went all official on me?

25:46.543 --> 25:48.476
EMT.

25:48.512 --> 25:49.644
I came from work.

25:49.679 --> 25:50.912
Mmm.

25:52.082 --> 25:53.982
You look good.

25:54.017 --> 25:56.951
Not much else to do
in there but work out.

25:56.987 --> 25:58.786
So what now?

25:58.822 --> 26:01.789
Laying low with my cellmate Damon.

26:01.814 --> 26:03.741
Mexican banger hit man motherfucker.

26:03.766 --> 26:05.999
[chuckles]

26:07.097 --> 26:09.697
Cops come talking to you?

26:09.733 --> 26:11.165
Think I'd snitch?

26:19.033 --> 26:21.184
Look, I'm, um...

26:22.612 --> 26:24.078
I'm getting some new IDs, some cash,

26:24.114 --> 26:26.309
and heading to Mexico.

26:26.334 --> 26:28.100
Wow.

26:28.351 --> 26:29.989
You should come.

26:32.556 --> 26:35.048
Come with you to Mexico?

26:35.792 --> 26:37.859
[laughs and scoffs]

26:42.194 --> 26:45.996
Thought a lot about you inside.

26:49.973 --> 26:52.674
You're under my skin,
man. The fuck can I do?

26:52.709 --> 26:55.176
Hmm?

26:55.211 --> 26:56.544
Can I do?

26:56.580 --> 26:57.712
[Damon whistles]

27:04.087 --> 27:05.386
Think about it.

27:09.459 --> 27:10.858
How am I gonna find you?

27:10.894 --> 27:12.048
Look up.

27:18.134 --> 27:22.203
[van door slides open, shuts]

27:22.228 --> 27:25.106
[engine revving]

27:25.141 --> 27:27.575
- [door bangs open]
- Hand over the cash

27:27.611 --> 27:29.644
and give us whatever's left in the safe!

27:29.679 --> 27:31.279
With a little more haste, honey!

27:31.314 --> 27:32.480
Or what? You gonna shoot me?

27:34.150 --> 27:36.084
Oh, what, it's bulletproof?

27:36.086 --> 27:37.418
I'm insulted!

27:37.454 --> 27:39.053
This is nothing but a window condom?

27:39.089 --> 27:41.089
between you and the
people of this community.

27:41.124 --> 27:42.557
