than what we're doing!

27:50.533 --> 27:52.066
Frank.

27:52.102 --> 27:54.268
Look, everybody gets
robbed sooner or later.

27:54.304 --> 27:56.304
It's the only way to
balance out the economy.

27:56.339 --> 27:58.439
- Frank!
- Come on, be a team player,

27:58.475 --> 28:01.609
go raw, and just fork er the cash!

28:01.645 --> 28:03.144
Craig!

28:03.179 --> 28:05.413
