28:11.888 --> 28:13.254
What... uh... this is a...

28:13.289 --> 28:14.756
Pull, pull, pull it, pull!

28:14.791 --> 28:16.591
Oh, shit, go! Go! Go!

28:16.626 --> 28:18.126
