28:22.332 --> 28:24.666
Hi. How wasted was Lip?

28:24.701 --> 28:26.267
Very.

28:26.302 --> 28:27.737
Should we be worried?

28:27.762 --> 28:28.928
Yeah. We should.

28:30.073 --> 28:31.592
[Kev] Wow!

28:31.617 --> 28:33.608
This place really turned around, huh?

28:33.643 --> 28:34.942
